{"tid":2217590,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"612 reminder：香港冇「認罪師」","createTime":"2020-09-25T14:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T14:52:47.000Z","uid":313334,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"afd9bc7a29fda43ad0d4313b5c23674d72f9d9b3","tid":2217590,"uid":313334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:18:41.000Z","msg":"【法律知識：香港冇「認罪師」】<br />\n<br />\n背景費事講，明就明。純粹針對某啲人指「聲稱XX案被捕人士係手足就係幫被捕人士認罪。」呢type言論。<br />\n<br />\n就算係招認口供都唔代表認罪（當然你唔遵守「我冇嘢講」會帶黎非常多麻煩）。<br />\n<br />\n記住「認罪」得一個情況：就係你喺法庭話你認罪。<br />\n<br />\n即使係疑似被告家屬朋友、知情者係某某論壇講出任何可能有關案件嘅事，<br />\n係警方調查角度上：可能會有作用。<br />\n但係法庭角度上：呢啲證明唔到係佢本人講既言論冇咩可能呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n更何況只係一班食花生嘅群眾係到留言稱呼某某係「手足」，根本無傷大雅。<br />\n<br />\n最後，「有軍火庫係鬼」、「大遊行前拉人係劇本」、「真手足唔會持有胡椒槍」呢種言論只會顯出自己嘅無知，而且呢啲言論對成件事都無任何作用。<br />\n<br />\n#法律及被捕須知<br />\n<br />\n原文link： <a href=\"https://t.me/reminder612/26866\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Freminder612%2F26866&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=b9824e5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/reminder612/26866</a>"},{"pid":"5712c3f5892a4fe68b0fcec6ff44f3af4b5f4216","tid":2217590,"uid":313334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b9f16f6a692bbee507cd2a11b4889e66ac05e8","tid":2217590,"uid":266294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828bdff65003021cd8f3f16f74e811f0dc91d3b2","tid":2217590,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d93e661b7eaa35749efefccca97de0379412b81","tid":2217590,"uid":262406,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4tQ8Ok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4tQ8Ok.jpg&h=0eb028ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48db8b5f81090164b263414cce83f1359980062d","tid":2217590,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"25f94023554c3ca698e639373cd1d022419dee99","tid":2217590,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f192a7e58690f804783889dae51615205d316966","tid":2217590,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"037c8d20edd3ef95a45c4b22a1bb8fa5ae55315f","tid":2217590,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:23:34.000Z","msg":"班cctoy戇鳩仲日日喺度話咩唔好幫人認罪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10e5768da69fd40e7a26ab377dd542609038d73e","tid":2217590,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:23:48.000Z","msg":"有用po"},{"pid":"61498591ce07137249b9db8e883d332c759d4d0f","tid":2217590,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:25:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"226e104bfa3580f7b5ce7c8e689ea8845c6da814","tid":2217590,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aadb39eebff5acba3ce379dbd4bc710b4c9b649","tid":2217590,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:26:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c890f0634212044fc78fbb2674e90c8b4628eeef","tid":2217590,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:27:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dc8c110e9679ff07f75aa46372101d3e8c4efe76","tid":2217590,"uid":135274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:28:42.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"45473928df9b2f8db3671d014be536ab603e778c","tid":2217590,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:29:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb356bf7aacde2b3e5d7e317d584a6d27b78818e","tid":2217590,"uid":50521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0936eb3606c32562a0b282d05fb26200124ce777","tid":2217590,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:52:47.000Z","msg":"#散水論 #D016 #槍械 #炸藥<br />\n【散水論：搜到槍同炸藥係劇本！係自編自導！】<br />\n<br />\n敵人發動輿論機器去抹黑我哋手足嘅功勞，當一有手足失手因為槍械、炸藥失手被擒，打手就隨即湧現，用垃圾回覆洗版：<br />\n「次次都係呢個劇本」<br />\n「李桂華大導演」<br />\n「遊行前就會有槍」<br />\n「永遠有槍又唔用，都唔知有黎做乜」<br />\n「擺明老屈」<br />\n<br />\n民眾否認、甚至厭惡槍械嘅存在係幫政權維持穩定，相反支持手足廣泛使用槍械炸藥先係對政權有威脅。香港需要由香港人用武裝接管，而唔係單靠外國制裁，而打破香港秩序最需要嘅就係民間武裝。打手點解要洗板強調係「劇本」同「自編自導」？因為可以不斷削弱大眾對槍械同炸藥嘅正當性同接受程度。風向撚將槍械同炸藥由大眾嘅思想抹走，咁槍械炸藥自然會喺香港絕跡。同時，依啲回覆令當刻正為軍火籌措嘅手足心灰意冷，打擊我哋陣營士氣。<br />\n<br />\n打手另一方面又會好言相勸，用嘅藉口不外乎：「曱甴眾多，得一把槍有咩用」、「藏槍好危險，不如去做twitter師安全啲」。我哋舊文已經提過[1]，政權最懼怕嘅就係公民武裝嘅出現，當家家戶戶都有槍械，規模不論孤狼抑或小隊，甚至係民兵組織，曱甴喺大街窄巷隨時被民眾射殺，社會秩序自然瓦解。<br />\n<br />\n自2015年起有無數手足為槍械炸藥而奔走，呢班英雄被抹黑做「鬼」，到今時今日仲有人喺連登帶風向去抹黑其他手足。如果你自認唔係打手，但係就曾經發表過上述言論，咁你必須反省一下，問下自己呢一年幾嚟，有冇真正理解革命嘅目的與意義，否則你只會淪為政權嘅幫兇。<br />\n<br />\n我哋要一一駁斥自欺欺人嘅想法，欺凌同排斥散播失敗主義嘅「旁觀者」，令佢哋成為社會不受歡迎嘅一群。即使群眾無手足嘅勇氣去運軍火，我哋都應該鼓勵群眾喺唔同崗位出力，和平嘅就捐錢俾手足用嚟買軍火，或者俾事敗嘅手足做安家費，進步嘅就為搜購同使用軍火親力親為。手足為組織公民武裝貢獻良多，我哋喺度向手足致敬！<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n[1]思想武裝：擴闊對武力嘅想像<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmanual/165\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmanual%2F165&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=30468c7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmanual/165</a><br />\n===<br />\n舊文重溫：<br />\n散水論：咪屈手足藏槍啦／做乜要幫手足認藏槍？<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkmanual/306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkmanual%2F306&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzoMY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=9b9742cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkmanual/306</a><br />\n===<br />\n圖片credit：流亡手足心事台<br />\n@hongkongerintheworld<br />\n===<br />\n請follow 《香港革命指南》<br />\n@hkmanual"}]}